{"tid":1390607,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港的「小朋友」 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-07-31T07:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T08:31:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ce053cc3c78e22a373c78431b5f9c8ffd75a6e83","tid":1390607,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190731/20740224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190731%2F20740224&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnaNFN85aI5NoQ2W41nR4Hcs%3D&h=26c7f508\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190731%2F20740224&h=ba5ad517\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190731/20740224</a><br />\n<br />\n香港的「小朋友」 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190731/large/1564470074_cb48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190731%2Flarge%2F1564470074_cb48.jpg&h=6f617a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n在網絡看到有人呼籲送物資、現金券給前線的「小朋友」，原來，這些「小朋友」們用盡積蓄購買裝備給自己，以及同路的朋友，已經山窮水盡。散場後若能安全回家的，家中藍絲父母也不會留飯。有「小朋友」貼文向在茶餐廳默默替他埋單，以及請他一起吃宵夜的大人道謝，看了令人心酸。<br />\n<br />\n這些「小朋友」們，多數在97前後出生，大一點的在讀大學，不少是中學生，7.27元朗事件中的傷者，最年輕的才15歲！暑假，這個年齡段的孩子們本該躲在冷氣房中打機、去外國旅遊，或者打暑期工儲錢，買自己心愛之物。晚上，美少女們應該攬着毛公仔睡覺。又或者已經開始拍拖，為一點點小事揑男朋友耳朵&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">時局動盪，香港淪陷，這些孩子們用稚弱雙肩扛起與他們的身軀絕不相稱的責任，走到了煙火最前線。他們流血、受傷、被捕，甚至做好了犧牲的準備，身上帶着遺書，還承受家人不理解的壓力，以及經濟困擾。還有，對自己的前途，以及香港前途的絕望。</span></span>即使在這樣的黑暗深淵，他們仍展現人性中最美好的一面，他們拿走木板車上的紙皮時，留下20元港幣及一張字條：「對不起我們取走了你的紙皮，這20元是給你的。」<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">這正是他們用生命竭力維護的東西：香港的法律、制度，香港人恪守的道德、良知，香港人珍視的人的尊嚴，包括對自己及對他人的尊重。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有經濟能力的，請設法援助「小朋友」。兄弟爬山，用各自的方法。  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n北京等運到 (馮睎乾)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n引刀成一快 (古德明)"},{"pid":"2d95100b2a070c6f1227610f6f7bdd0cabfe9a44","tid":1390607,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c7b5b6c76fa5f5cf120adf2a5d219c3dc0be85","tid":1390607,"uid":219244,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:44:20.000Z","msg":"我地係被時代選中嘅細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads//2014/10/891422_1396281450596766_1542195699_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F%2F2014%2F10%2F891422_1396281450596766_1542195699_n.jpg&h=83d706b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f376fdb76a411a088afac240c539479faf89178e","tid":1390607,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce053cc3c78e22a373c78431b5f9c8ffd75a6e83","tid":1390607,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190731/20740224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flif